channel.title: Hinata, which is better?
channel.description:
Me and my stupid little brother made 2 drawings of Hinata, we, I mean, I, know they both suck, but the bastard thinks he is some kind off genius artist and that he will be famous one day.
[b](both were drawn in 15 minutes)[/b]
[b]Picture 1:[/b] [img]http://i.imgur.com/Xo1C1.jpg[/img]
[b]Picture 2:[/b] [img]http://i.imgur.com/xNRjI.jpg[/img]
All I'm asking is which one is better? (Again, both suck, imo, but for my brother mine is horrible and his is on a completely different level.)
Here's the original: [img]http://alblack.files.wordpress.com/2009/07/222180hinata-preocupada.jpg[/img]
